TuxCut Version 4.0
==================
Features:
  - Scan your network for live hosts and list with hostnames.
  - Protect your linux box from any arp spoof attack (like netcut).
  - Change the MAC address of ur network adapter.
  - Arpspoof any of the computers connected to your network.


Dependancy : 
============
  - python 
  - PyQt4
  - arptables
  - arp-scan

Warning :
=========
Don't change you MAC address if you connect via wireless network with WPA/WPA2 encryption